name: Limited Edition: "Death or Glory" Skate Deck
description:
Limited Edition: "Death or Glory" Skate Deck 
$119.99 + $15 postage Australia wide ($20 intl)

Each deck will be personalised with your "word" or "name" of choice and individually hand signed and numbered by artist.

NB: Once ordered, please email info@steenjones.com with what you'd like written in the banner.

ALL pre-orders will be shipped on Wednesday the 18th of December, to ensure they arrive before Christmas Australia-wide!

*The deck is made from 100% Canadian rock maple and manufactured by one of Australia's leading skateboard companies.

name: "Alphabet Flash"
description:
As you may or may not be aware, I'm currently in the process of painting this set of flash for Christmas, so right now you are pre-ordering and securing your print before they "officially" go on sale/sell out.

All pre-orders will be sent out on Friday the 13th to ensure they arrive in time and will each come with a few sticker just because!

A4 Print (297x210mm) 
-$20

A4 Original (297x210mm) 
-$100. Price includes registered post (+$10 for international)

*All prints are printed on premium 300GSM archival card. 
*Original is painted on ARCHES 100% cotton 300GSM watercolour paper and hand signed by artist.
*If you'd like more then 5, please email info@steenjones.com to discuss discount. Much love.

name: Custom Skateboard decks
description:
Skateboards rule, they're fun so I want to do as many as I can. 
If you'd like to discuss a personalised 1 of 1 deck for yourself, or loved one, then let's!

*Please note: As each board is different from one another, the price varies but start at $300.00 (deck included). That said - I'd prefer if you could email me first prior to purchasing so we can talk over your idea's and confirm a price before we start. 

Contact: steen@steenjones.com

name: Custom Mannequin Head/s
description:
I realise these technically isn't for sale BUT they're fun as hell so I'd love to do more, so if you'd like me to make a personalised for you or your loved one, then let's.

*Please note: As each head are different from one another, the price can from $200-$300 depending on the work and time involved. That said - I'd prefer if you could email me first prior to purchasing so we can talk over your idea's and confirm a price before we commence.

Contact: steen@steenjones.com
